{"tid":1598621,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"【澄清】國殤日黑汽球嘉年華活動","createTime":"2019-09-27T14:24:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T12:58:47.000Z","uid":133867,"like":21,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"1005581dafc5172579551525543a8d371bec2d2b","tid":1598621,"uid":133867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T14:24:32.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">我地明白哩個活動上有多次爭議同消息混亂，<br />\n<strong>抱歉我地資訊混亂，未能好好處理每個問題，在此我們先跟大家深深抱歉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n先重申我們主張民眾決定，對於放/不放氣球爭議<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><ins><span style=\"color: gold;\">我們不會放生汽球，因環境問題及國際關注！！請大家注意！</span></strong></ins></span><br />\n<br />\n我地喺連登及Twitter 等各media得知有意見反映，綜合各方意見後，以下為改善方案:<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><ins>一，改以爆波取代放波</span></strong></ins><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">十一國慶！賀佢老味！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n以爆波表達我們對政權不滿，不再畏怕！不再恐懼！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">準時八點爆佢！寓以支爆！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<em><span style=\"color: green;\">愛護環境人人有責，各位記得爆咗之後要執返啊！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而我地都會有義工幫手執返啲波</em></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">二，各位將汽球帶到十一各遊行及集會</span></strong></ins><br />\n將我地整場運動嘅代表色&mdash;&mdash;黑色，精神帶到不同地區，遍地開花<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">十月一日<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />七時集合<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n八時賀佢老味<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></div><br />\n<br />\n另外為免資訊混亂，我地亦開設咗TG channel:<br />\n <a href=\"https://t.me/BlackballonCarnival\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FBlackballonCarnival&d=MLRnjlmMEh1el5UvTt2rHZLurRSHZiEGX9rhKonVocs%3D&h=beb07c88\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/BlackballonCarnival</a><br />\n<br />\n公海TG:<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/GHCqykfGOOkvEdBAqj1nuA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FGHCqykfGOOkvEdBAqj1nuA&d=MLRnjlmMEh1el5UvTt2rHZLurRSHZiEGX9rhKonVocs%3D&h=d3a2623e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/GHCqykfGOOkvEdBAqj1nuA</a><br />\n<br />\n舊post:【突發】十一國殤日 第一炮 《黑色快閃嘉年華》<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1596691\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1596691</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: orange;\">希望十月一號可以見到各位散步，之後食早餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>再次抱歉我地資訊未能處理完善，我們亦會盡量妥當安排，令影響降至最低，我們明白這並非盡善盡美，不過我們會不停反省，不斷改進<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，希望會力臻完善！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />望請各位體諒</strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />感謝各方比意見我地！萬分感激！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4kL7NHT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4kL7NHT.jpg&h=0e93d554&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pP8tw9y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpP8tw9y.jpg&h=cf9d33b4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RnRKPWd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRnRKPWd.jpg&h=b9613388&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KsZMiPz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKsZMiPz.jpg&h=f5a16d9f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"609eaca925f8c402b7142c8865e94302e1a63972","tid":1598621,"uid":60434,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T14:26:03.000Z","msg":"嘉年華式抗爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e534fa64ae8ec692b53ddcff9cff284d8d27bd8","tid":1598621,"uid":53220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T14:27:10.000Z","msg":"支爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />賀佢老味"},{"pid":"97b7d8803dd8636722d71119bd697411e231b9c6","tid":1598621,"uid":102955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T14:27:43.000Z","msg":"賀佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a17364bf3190979e2682d8b65eebaad5c6e3ddde","tid":1598621,"uid":183142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T14:29:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7b0816d2ae49471d7e811ae1b136e07e8c07434","tid":1598621,"uid":183142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T14:29:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccb46d17089d9b3c2502893b8bf1823f2568158e","tid":1598621,"uid":183142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T14:29:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6defed87d1eb57feb77359772732b0fc2995ac1","tid":1598621,"uid":183142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T14:30:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c9fe759f064f06ed10ad8ea9164898cb26042e8","tid":1598621,"uid":288048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T14:30:32.000Z","msg":"推 拎黑汽球 不放生"},{"pid":"f3ac0cb9e63af0256e2b9e41e3378c4005f3ce15","tid":1598621,"uid":118652,"like":7,"dislike":0,"sc